      "updated": 1771307885705,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cache Architecture just define how our application actually interacts with the cache. And so \nspecifically, this is defining the order in which reads and writes happend between both of our\ncache and database and our application service. And so the most common caching pattern by far, \nthis is the one that we should default to in our interview is Cach Aside.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cache Architecture just define how our application actually interacts with the cache. And so \nspecifically, this is defining the order in which reads and writes happend between both of our\ncache and database and our application service. And so the most common caching pattern by far, \nthis is the one that we should default to in our interview is Cach Aside.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
