      "updated": 1771308578254,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Not technically a database, think of it as a database thats design specifically for Large files.\nand these large files commonly referred to as Binary large objects or blobs. But in reality they\nare things like video, images, music files, json files, large text files, all of these if we want\nto open in terminal, we will see this is just large collection of bytes, there is some often in \nthe order of MB(megabytes) that need to be stored somewhere. and thats where objects storage comes\ninto play.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Not technically a database, think of it as a database thats design specifically for Large files.\nand these large files commonly referred to as Binary large objects or blobs. But in reality they\nare things like video, images, music files, json files, large text files, all of these if we want\nto open in terminal, we will see this is just large collection of bytes, there is some often in \nthe order of MB(megabytes) that need to be stored somewhere. and thats where objects storage comes\ninto play.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
